Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.82,0:14:58.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是... 要‧我‧呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.74,0:15:03.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,織.. 不.. 晶...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.60,0:15:07.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了優介特別準備的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.50,0:15:09.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼.. 先作哪個?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.87,0:15:12.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當!! 當然是!!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.93,0:15:19.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在.. 這種地方...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.80,0:15:21.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼忍得住..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.07,0:15:38.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,優介... 要上了~~~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.71,0:15:40.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,優介..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.28,0:15:54.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗚嗚嗚 T_T
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.26,0:15:57.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明天加油吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.07,0:16:07.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.04,0:16:16.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早啊 助理監督
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.32,0:16:18.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼三崎小姐會在這裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.00,0:16:23.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個.. 是我的問題嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.66,0:16:27.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,優介和女演員三崎小姐是朋友 真了不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.80,0:16:31.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是.. 為什麼來這裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.57,0:16:35.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,優介不是代替監督進行演技指導嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.40,0:16:38.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,了不起了不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.07,0:16:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,優介 加油啊! 我幫你加油!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.50,0:16:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託了 監督
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.35,0:16:45.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是助理監督!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.21,0:16:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且今天也要攝影...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.20,0:16:48.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,唉呀? 你沒聽到嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.83,0:16:51.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為監督的緣故 今天不攝影了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.84,0:16:53.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦? 是這樣嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.78,0:16:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉 實際上是因為昨天公園的事情 被娛樂周刊的人拍到照片了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.60,0:17:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想來和你道歉 所以拜託事務所停止了攝影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.48,0:17:05.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.95,0:17:13.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼 我還有很多事情要做 加油了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.06,0:17:15.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.44,0:17:19.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能妨礙優介啊 這也是實現夢想的第一步哦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.41,0:17:21.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我怎麼能不幫忙呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.00,0:17:29.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你.. 到底是..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.25,0:17:34.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做..做什麼..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.46,0:17:35.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裡是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.13,0:17:39.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裡是夫婦神聖的場所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.82,0:17:42.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以對我有意義...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.96,0:17:55.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住手!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.36,0:17:58.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳到底在想什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.56,0:18:02.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是剛和晶結婚的新人助理監督
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.24,0:18:06.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在演藝界或許有各式各樣的規矩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.28,0:18:08.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但也不要拿這些來為難我!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.33,0:18:13.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳不也是為了昨天的事情... 來道歉的..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.50,0:18:33.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是男人吧? 讓我看看你像個男人的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.98,0:19:03.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊! 不行! 馬上就...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.58,0:19:06.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳是來誘惑我的吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.17,0:19:14.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.45,0:19:17.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要緊 繼續...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.51,0:19:46.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要..要射出來了..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.88,0:19:48.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我..我也...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.46,0:20:00.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要..要射..出去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.18,0:20:03.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,晶!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.60,0:20:20.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,溫子.. 是第一次做啊..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.39,0:20:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉... 已經很久沒有插入了..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.50,0:20:26.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,射在裡面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.13,0:20:29.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在說什麼啊? 和太太一直都在做還...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.23,0:20:35.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果懷孕了 我也沒辦法負責 是妳來誘惑我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.43,0:20:37.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,變冷淡了呢..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.92,0:20:38.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.33,0:20:42.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的事情...
