Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.04,0:21:49.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在打掃的時候笨手笨腳的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.32,0:21:52.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要緊吧? 沒受傷吧?
