Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.66,0:21:59.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,優介
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.61,0:22:00.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,晶..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.88,0:22:01.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯?
