Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:12.84,0:24:15.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,晶也...夾得我很緊很緊啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:16.15,0:24:18.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能一起做真好!
